verse.lines:
{lang-eng}Asleep in Jesus, blessed sleep
From which none ever wakes to weep;
A calm and undisturbed repose,
Unbroken by the last of foes.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Asleep in Jesus, peaceful rest,
Hence waking we're supremly blest;
No fear, no woe, shall dim that hour.
That manifests the Savior's pow'r.{/lang-eng}
